%F A033305 a(n) = h(n) - h(n-1), n>0, h(n) = Sum_{k=1..n} (Sum_{r=0..k} (C(k,r)*Sum_{m=0..r}(C(r,m)*Sum_{j=0..m} C(m,j)*C(j,n-m-k-j-r)*(-1)^(n-m-k-j-r) ))). - _Vladimir Kruchinin_, Sep 10 2010
